data.title: Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge – Big Ed
data.text:
The World’s First Dual Edge Display

The Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge gives you an experience like no other. With vivid colors and dramatic contrast bursting from its screen, This is the brightest, most vibrant screen you’ve ever seen. And it’s as sophisticated and elegant as it is smart.

The Fast Charge Experience

Get introduced to the new standard in charging with the amazing Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge. Fast Charge for 10 minutes to get up to 4 hours of use. Or charge wirelessly for 100% of the charge with 0% outlet. Running low? Use Ultra Power Saving Mode.

Clarity with S6 Edge; 16MP Camera

Tired of blurry images, red-dot eyes and unworthy “selfie” moments? The Galaxy S6 edge features intuitive front and rear cameras that let you capture every moment with exceptional clarity and achieve brilliant photos in any light and because timing is everything, a simple ‘double tap’ launches the camera in under a second so that precious moments aren’t lost – but shared.

Keep It Locked with Samsung S6 Edge!

S6 Edge securely keep your data safe. You’ll love the security as much as the design. From the simple, touch-based fingerprint recognition to the built-in malware protection, it knows how to look after itself – and you. And that means less worrying, more living.
